ional anthem months before it attained full independence from the UK.\", \"from\": 5799, \"to\": 5999, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5996, \"end\": 5998, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9999999907176971, \"rank\": 8.4880229217953e-09, \"text\": \"UK\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Federation\", \"from\": 5814, \"to\": 5828}, {\"ngram\": \"St. Kitts\", \"from\": 5832, \"to\": 5841}, {\"ngram\": \"Nevis\", \"from\": 5846, \"to\": 5851}, {\"ngram\": \"an island nation\", \"from\": 5853, \"to\": 5869}, {\"ngram\": \"the eastern Caribbean\", \"from\": 5873, \"to\": 5894}, {\"ngram\": \"a competition\", \"from\": 5901, \"to\": 5914}, {\"ngram\": \"a national anthem months\", \"from\": 5925, \"to\": 5949}, {\"ngram\": \"full independence\", \"from\": 5969, \"to\": 5986}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Artist and musician Kenrick Georges decided to write and compose an entry at 2 a.m. on the day of the deadline-March 31-and completed it at 6 a.m., according to localmedia.\", \"from\": 6001, \"to\": 6173, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"musician Kenrick Georges\", \"from\": 6012, \"to\": 6036}, {\"ngram\": \"an entry\", \"from\": 6066, \"to\": 6074}, {\"ngram\": \"2 a.m.\", \"from\": 6078, \"to\": 6084}, {\"ngram\": \"the day\", \"from\": 6088, \"to\": 6095}, {\"ngram\": \"the deadline-March\", \"from\": 6099, \"to\": 6117}, {\"ngram\": \"localmedia\", \"from\": 6162, \"to\": 6172}]}, {\"sentence\": \"An hour later, he asked a piano teacher to play it for him, and he submitted a recording of the song on a cassette tape later that day.\", \"from\": 6174, \"to\": 6309, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a piano teacher\", \"from\": 6198, \"to\": 6213}, {\"ngram\": \"a recording\", \"from\": 6251, \"to\": 6262}, {\"ngram\": \"the song\", \"from\": 6266, \"to\": 6274},